A Heroku buildpack for Perl + pmbp
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This is a Heroku buildpack to run a Perl application using the pmbp.pl tool <https://github.com/wakaba/perl-setupenv>.

The latest version is available at: <https://github.com/wakaba/heroku-buildpack-perl-pmbp>.

